s on me since when I die all my stuff is on my corpse.  Something I always like to have on me is invis potions though...<br><br>Q: Was the warrior class the first character you seriously played?<br><br>Warrior is the only class I have seriously played.  I have not gotten another class character above level 5.<br><br>Q: I'm sure you have had plenty of fun throughout, but what particular moment really stood out that made you cackle evilly at your own power?<br><br>Soloing Lord Garlic (forget his real name) the goblin guy in Lake of Ill Omen who used to drop the Mith Staff.  I soloed him when he was still worth experience to me which is saying something when he is a shaman with a pet.<br><br>Q: If you could add one spell type or ability to the Everquest warrior class, what would it be?(just ONE hehe)<br><br>I would love to see a weapon/shield combo that makes using a shield feasible.  Maybe on the Plane of War in planes of power that guy who has a weapon and a shield will have a combo useable by a warrior.  Would be neat to have it so they equipped together only -- for example a 27 damage/15 delay sword with Enraging Blow to ensure that all important hate list position and a shield that is like 250 AC, 500 HP, +15 Sta/Str/Dex/Agi/all resists.  That would definitely be worthy to wear over traditional 1hers.<br><br>Q: Do you solo regularly?<br><br>Yes.  I have soloed every level from about 14-60.  Not always for a lot of experience, but at least one blue of experience per level was earned solo.  Sometimes 3 yellows...<br><br>Q: If you could trade your warrior character for any other class of the same level and relatively equal gear, would you?<br><br>Nope. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=20383">Hulanta</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uvaraho1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Varaho1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>