at was a big deal back then.<br><br>Q: I'm sure you have had plenty of fun throughout, but what particular moment really stood out that made you cackle evilly at your own power?<br>Yeah. One time a few weeks ago I was fully raid buffed, and bored, and went to hang out in Velks. Well, I was invis, and fell into lower dogs somehow. On my way out, I was seen, so I hit defensive and ran to castle... Since I didn't want to train Upper Dogs, I ran out the back way, through velks throne room. I hopped off CE and zoned out, but it was too late. Fully 2/3rds of the mobs in the zone were roaming around the bottom floor slaughtering everyone. About 30 deaths and5 survivors... After dying with laughter, I zoned back in, invis again, and sat out to watch the CR. Apperantly, velks two guards, the Crystal Guardian's, loved that zone in. They were stuck behind it. So every 5 minutes for half the night, they came out and killed a few people at the zone in randomly. One person in particular that I didn't like died immediately after getting res, before even looting one item. Looking back, I regret it somewhat, but damn that was a nice train.<br><br>Q: If you could add one spell type or ability to the Everquest warrior class, what would it be?(just ONE hehe)<br>Death Touch.. or Complete Heal.<br><br>Q: Do you solo regularly?<br>Not any more, but I did a lot from 40 to 55..<br><br>Q: If you could trade your warrior character for any other class of the same level and relatively equal gear, would you?<br>Not really.. <p>Veteran Fulorian Cavestomper <BR>60th Warlord of Xegony<BR>Val'Kori</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/umegadyens.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Megadyen S</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/4/02 9:40:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarri